<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The Bachelor's Bella Varelis has shared the heartbreaking news that her grandfather has died of lung cancer.</p>

<p>During Wednesday nigh't episode of the show, psychic medium Alison Maiden informed the reality star that she was sensing the spirit of an older man with cancer.</p>

<p>Posting to Instagram on Friday, the 25-year-old revealed that her grandad passed just a few weeks after the reading.</p>

<p>Sad news: The Bachelor's Bella Varelis has shared the heartbreaking news that her grandfather has died of lung cancer. Pictured Bella and Locky Gilbert </p>

<p>'Overwhelmed and beyond grateful for the love and messages I've been receiving. Unfortunately, my grandfather did end up passing away a couple weeks later,' she wrote. </p>

<p>The reality star explained that she was able 'be home' with her family when it happened due to the COVID-19 lockdowns. </p>

<p>'And due to the covid lockdown, I thankfully got to be home with my family and know he will always be looking over me.' </p>

<p>She went on to say that the psychic reading was an 'emotional whirlwind' but she was lucky that Locky Gilbert was there to 'support' her.  </p>

<p>Prediction: Psychic medium Alison Maiden (pictured) dropped by the mansion on Wednesday's episode, where things took a heartbreaking turn as she informed Bella that she was sensing the spirit of an older man with cancer</p>

<p>'This moment was such an emotional whirlwind for me and I wasn't expecting Locky to come and find me, but having him there was exactly the support I needed' she told her fans. </p>

<p>On Wednesday night's episode Bella broke down into tears after hearing Allison's psychic reading. </p>

<p>'I have an older man in the spirit world here. I'm getting a feeling it's someone with cancer - he's telling me,' she told the brunette.</p>

<p>The look on Bella's face quickly crumbled, as she responded: 'My grandfather, he has cancer... I'm not sure if he's passed. He had lung cancer before I left [to film for the show].'</p>

<p>Upsetting: Bella (left) broke down into tears as she revealed her grandfather has been diagnosed with lung cancer before she left for the show. Pictured with Izzy Sharman-Firth</p>

<p>Speaking to the producers, a crushed Bella said: 'The way Alison spoke about my grandfather made me think that he may have passed while I been in here, and I kind of just started to tear up.'</p>

<p>The scene cut back to the psychic reading where a teary-eyed Bella was comforted by Locky and the fellow girls.</p>

<p>Bella then told cameras: 'I think something has happened, and I may need to go home. I need to call mum. I need to find out if my grandfather is okay.'</p>

<p>Following the phone call, Bella learnt that her grandfather was at the time alive and doing fine.</p>

<p>The Bachelor continues Wednesday at 7:30pm on Channel Ten.  </p>

<p>Confirmation: Following the phone call, Bella learnt that her grandfather was at the time alive and doing fine </p>
